                        {
                            "key": "XT-25754",
                            "title": "Notification history improvements",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>On the <b>Notification history</b> page, you can view statuses at-a-glance with color-coded messages. You can search or filter by status for finance, integration with Sage Intacct objects, and stock.</p><p>The <b>Finance</b> and <b>Stock</b> tabs include document links for easy-access.</p><p>The <b>Integration status</b> tab was moved from the <b>Sage Intacct integration</b> page.</p>",
